g":"香港開埠以來首個雙胞胎會議<br />\n淋病可以名留青屎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"你忘記左臨立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"臨立會唔係在深圳開？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"臨立會只著眼處理過渡事宜，民意並不在考慮範圍中。<br />\n<br />\n1998年，臨立會通過將立法會選舉制度，由單議席單票制改為比例代表制，按照名單得票比例分配議席，及引入最大餘額法──把名單上已獲取議席的票數減去，再把各名單的剩餘票數從多至少順序，餘額多者可獲議席。李鵬飛表示，改行比例代表制是臨立會與中央政府商討出來的結果，目的為制衡民主黨，避免他們控制議會。此選舉制度亦沿用至今。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/127_pol2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2F127_pol2%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=b52f0f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/127_pol2/</a>"},{"pid":"302194b6abb4739fc3f8fc1773d364de7046dfbd","tid":1141140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10edfa3be949056f3b3d071b19a9373a0d8a49e0","tid":1141140,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"垃會秘書長面書確認會議面書紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/9yDXta5.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yDXta5.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=b1654b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/9yDXta5.png[/img］</a>"},{"pid":"a94bb6